      "textIndopak": "فَذٰلِكَ الَّذِىۡ يَدُعُّ الۡيَتِيۡمَۙ‏",
      "words": [
        {
          "position": 1,
          "textUthmani": "فَذَٰلِكَ",
          "transliteration": "fadhālika",
          "translation": "Then that",
